W: Why didn’t you attend the dinner party last night?
M: I had to rush home to babysit my kids.
W: Really? Couldn’t your wife have watched them?
M:                                              
2. [출제의도] 짧은 응답 표현하기
M: Mom, you know I’m going to the observatory 
at Alden mountain tonight.
W: I’m afraid that it might be cold at the top. 
Make sure to bring your hat and gloves.
M: Okay, but I can’t find my red coat. Do you 
know where it is?
